abcasm is an ABC assembler.

Usage: see abcasm.sh

Syntax: the assembler language is based on abcdump's output format.

Hacking:

1. The new  ABCasm4 (ABC Assembler) can be built from here: //depot/skunkworks/tharwood/aetapps/ABCasm4/ and is dependent on the 

2. Add the paths to the classes and libs locations in a build.properties file, e.g.
    abct.lib.dir=/Users/bsahlas/depot/flashide/trunk/compiler/com.adobe.flash.compiler/generated/dist/sdk/lib
    compiler.classpath=/Users/bsahlas/depot/flashide/trunk/compiler/com.adobe.flash.compiler/generated/intermediates/classes
    abct.home=/Users/bsahlas/depot/flashide/trunk/compiler/com.adobe.flash.compiler
3. build it "ant"

